abstract="This paper analyzes the trend of moving from Internet of Things to a new vision, Web of Things. The objective is to have a deep look into the demands of future Internet of Things, in order to identify key research issues for the emerging Web of Things. A selected use case, BAS-AMI is described in the paper, to help understand the identified research issues.",
