abstract="In this article we have proposed a novel method for ECG signal processing in biometric applications. The main idea is to correct anomalies in various segments of ECG waveform rather than skipping a corrupted ECG heartbeat, as it is commonly done in most cases. The proposed approach is taking into consideration that biosignals are of quasi-periodic nature.",
